    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a major project. The engine is currently running poorly with a persistent misfire, and the transmission slips significantly when shifting into higher gears. The body has several areas of rust and a cracked windshield, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear throughout. It is sold as-is and will likely need to be towed.",
